                   (2.27)          (1.99)   

freedomtom~s        2.010***        2.010***
                   (4.06)          (4.20)   

generosity          0.364           0.364   
                   (1.13)          (1.02)   

perception~n       -0.605*         -0.605   
                  (-2.08)         (-1.73)   

_cons              -2.237***       -2.237** 
                  (-3.55)         (-3.09)   
